<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When loading your own view plugins in module.config:</p>

<pre class="literal">'view_manager' =&gt; array(
   'helper_map' =&gt; array(
        'hello' =&gt; 'MyNamespace\View\Helper\Hello',
    ),
    // [snip]
),</pre>

<p>Zend\Mvc\View::getHelperLoader() reports:</p>

<p>````</p>

<p>$map = $this-&gt;config['helper_map'] is a Zend\Config\Config and not array.</p>

<p>$map-&gt;toArray(); fixes the issue.</p>

